# Complete Azure DevOps Team Example

This fixture demonstrates team memberships and administrators.

## Features

- Creates a single Azure DevOps team
- Applies member and administrator assignments
- Uses the project-level "Readers" group for members to keep membership scope small

## Key Configuration

Use this fixture to validate membership and admin assignments.

## Usage

```bash
terraform init
terraform plan
terraform apply
```

## Cleanup

```bash
terraform destroy
```
